===Noun===
'''turnbuckle'''
# A [[coupling]] device consisting of two [[eyelets]] or other connection points connected [[screw]] [[threads]].  The joint in between can be turned to shorten or lengthen the device with [[mechanical advantage]] provided by the screw threads.
# {{nautical}} A [[link]] [[threaded]] on both ends of a short [[bar]] which is used to pull objects together. {{FM 55-501)